&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Fulfillment Specialist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are seeking a highly organized and proactive Order Fulfillment Specialist to join our&amp;nbsp;team and take charge of maintaining relationships with our customer pipeline while&amp;nbsp;driving revenue growth. The ideal candidate will possess strong communication skills,&amp;nbsp;exceptional attention to detail, and a proven track record in project management and&amp;nbsp;customer relationship management.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are open to candidates who are willing to work Mountain Time Zone (MST/MDT) hours.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Impact You Will Make&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Conduct post-fulfillment surveys and communication to ensure customer&amp;nbsp;satisfaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Implement and maintain a structured communication plan, including 30-60-90&amp;nbsp;day and ongoing communication with sold customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Offer products and services during monthly check-ins, responsible for generating&amp;nbsp;new Monthly Recurring Revenue (MRR).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Manage contract renewals as customer contracts expire, ensuring retention and&amp;nbsp;customer satisfaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Increase fulfillment rates by managing orders from inception to&amp;nbsp;completion/installation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Efficiently enter orders into the back-office system, ensuring accuracy and&amp;nbsp;timeliness.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Set milestones and proactively reach out to suppliers for updates to ensure&amp;nbsp;timely delivery and installation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Utilize SMS/email systems to send reminders to customers regarding milestone&amp;nbsp;updates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Proactively resolve cancellations by addressing customer concerns and finding&amp;nbsp;solutions to retain their business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
